description: From the minute all of the hot guys of "Fire Island Cruising 05" board the ferry over to Fire Island, all of the fun spearheaded by Michael Lucas begins, but is no where near ending! Catch a glimpse into the photo shoots, pre-production, and post-production that goes into filming a steamy porn movie set on one of America's hottest gay getaways!
title: Go Behind the Scenes of "Fire Island Cruising 05"
